1
00:00:12,870 --> 00:00:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Anyone Who Says I'm Flat-Chested 
Needs to Step in a Pile of Dog Poop."</i></font>

2
00:00:16,830 --> 00:00:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've waited so long for this to come out.</i></font>

3
00:00:18,990 --> 00:00:20,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Summer vacation's almost over,</i></font>

4
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so I wanna get home and enjoy what's left 
of it reading in an air-conditioned room.</i></font>

5
00:01:58,410 --> 00:02:01,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home, big brother! 
We have a situation!</font>

6
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Kaju? Why are you so upset?</font>

7
00:02:03,930 --> 00:02:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an emergency! We need to 
schedule an interview immediately!</font>

8
00:02:07,270 --> 00:02:09,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Or should we just conduct one right now?</font>

9
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Take a deep breath.</font>

10
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once you've calmed down, 
tell me what happened.</font>

11
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! I have calmed down!</font>

12
00:02:16,820 --> 00:02:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She showed up without warning 
while I was preparing lunch!</font>

13
00:02:19,790 --> 00:02:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Lunch today is 
leftover curry from yesterday!</font>

14
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, she hasn't calmed down at all.</i></font>

15
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, at least I know what's for... lunch...</font>

16
00:02:31,980 --> 00:02:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be.</font>

17
00:02:35,020 --> 00:02:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Nukumizu-kun! Long time no see!</font>

18
00:02:37,510 --> 00:02:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This curry is so good. Don't they say 
curry tastes better on the second day?</font>

19
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Yanami-san, why are you 
in my house eating curry?</font>

20
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:48,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't talk with your mouth full!</i></font>

21
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:53,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I've been visiting all my friends
 to give them somen noodles.</font>

22
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="10"><b><font color="#23273b">Grandmother's
\h\hThreads</font></b></font></font></font>

23
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="10"><b><font color="#23273b">Highest Quality</font></b></font></font></font>

24
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="10"><b><font color="#23273b">Grandmother's
\h\hThreads</font></b></font></font></font>

25
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="10"><b><font color="#23273b">Highest Quality</font></b></font></font></font>

26
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:58,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you have so much somen?</font>

27
00:02:58,940 --> 00:03:02,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad's salary was paid in somen this month.</font>

28
00:03:04,940 --> 00:03:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His salary? What's going on?</font>

29
00:03:07,540 --> 00:03:12,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some stuff happened, and he 
got all of his July pay in somen.</font>

30
00:03:12,790 --> 00:03:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we have tons of somen at home. 
Like, a street value of 300,000 yen.</font>

31
00:03:16,810 --> 00:03:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Somen" isn't some codeword, is it?
 Is this stuff legal?</font>

32
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="20"><b><font color="#23273b">Grandmother's
\h\h\h\h\hThreads</font></b></font></font></font>

33
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:23,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course it is! What kind of family 
do you think I'm from, exactly?</font>

34
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I've eaten it. A lifetime's worth.</font>

35
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't really get it, but I think I got it.</i></font>

36
00:03:30,230 --> 00:03:31,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want some more curry?</font>

37
00:03:31,450 --> 00:03:33,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was my third plate. I'm good now.</font>

38
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You weren't on your second?</i></font>

39
00:03:40,670 --> 00:03:45,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Yanami-san. Would you mind 
if I asked you a few things?</font>

40
00:03:47,870 --> 00:03:48,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="16"><b><font color="#777a77">Start Recording</font></b></font></font>

41
00:03:48,180 --> 00:03:48,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="16"><b><font color="#51000b">Recording</font></b></font></font>

42
00:03:49,450 --> 00:03:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First of all, your date of birth and blood type.</font>

43
00:03:52,250 --> 00:03:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your family structure, hobbies, and skills. 
And when did you start seeing my big brother?</font>

44
00:03:56,130 --> 00:04:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, look. Yanami-san's really busy. 
Can't you save this for another time?</font>

45
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:04,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But dear brother, I need her to 
tell me stories about your school.</font>

46
00:04:05,070 --> 00:04:09,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nukumizu-kun, you make 
her call you "dear brother"?</font>

47
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't <i>make</i> her call me that!
 There's a difference!</font>

48
00:04:21,400 --> 00:04:24,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Comfortably lukewarm with 
just the perfect whiff of chlorine.</i></font>

49
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The tap water during summer 
vacation is something special.</i></font>

50
00:04:33,210 --> 00:04:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, is that you, Shikiya-senpai?</font>

51
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:40,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you must be... the boy 
from the literature club?</font>

52
00:04:40,090 --> 00:04:40,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

53
00:04:41,170 --> 00:04:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's she doing here?</i></font>

54
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:48,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came for something to drink,
 but I ran out of energy.</font>

55
00:04:52,150 --> 00:04:53,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go.</font>

56
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:57,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tip it for me.</font>

57
00:04:57,020 --> 00:04:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Huh?</font>

58
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:03,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up.</font>

59
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:17,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What in the world am I doing here?</i></font>

60
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:20,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

61
00:05:20,890 --> 00:05:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brought me back to life.</font>

62
00:05:24,170 --> 00:05:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way...</font>

63
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:30,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard Koto-san and Tamaki-san 
started dating. Is it true?</font>

64
00:05:30,930 --> 00:05:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Uh, yes. It is.</font>

65
00:05:35,370 --> 00:05:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it is?</font>

66
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:44,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Man, she's scary!</i></font>

67
00:05:44,570 --> 00:05:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="13"><font color="#111b10">Absent Today</font></font></font>

68
00:05:44,820 --> 00:05:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, should we get down to business?</font>

69
00:05:47,030 --> 00:05:49,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We actually got a notice 
from the student council.</font>

70
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:50,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The student council?</font>

71
00:05:51,050 --> 00:05:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All clubs are required to report 
their activities over summer vacation.</font>

72
00:05:56,810 --> 00:06:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I wanted to 
talk to you all about today.</font>

73
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But summer vacation's almost over. Why now?</font>

74
00:06:03,970 --> 00:06:06,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why now? Well...</font>

75
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't have a choice. I was busy 
with driving school and forgot all about it.</font>

76
00:06:11,210 --> 00:06:12,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What about entrance exams?</i></font>

77
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:13,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So here's my idea:</font>

78
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we take the web novels we wrote before 
and make them into a book. How's that sound?</font>

79
00:06:19,330 --> 00:06:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's a sample.</font>

80
00:06:21,210 --> 00:06:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font color="#216991">m 420 20 l 610 20 610 80 420 80</font></font>

81
00:06:21,210 --> 00:06:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="26"><font color="#eaead5">Is It More Painful 
to Be the Person 
Who Waits 
or the Person 
Who Sleeps Alone?

<font size="18">(All Ages)</font></font></font></b></font></font>

82
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What kind of sample is that?</i></font>

83
00:06:23,070 --> 00:06:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! I'll write the next part 
of the one I wrote at camp.</font>

84
00:06:27,130 --> 00:06:28,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will you write, Komari-chan?</font>

85
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="30"><font color="#23251f">A new work</font></font></font></font>

86
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A new work?</font>

87
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure go all-out, Komari-chan. 
You, Nukumizu-kun?</font>

88
00:06:37,170 --> 00:06:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

89
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I guess I could revise the first part 
of <i>Halfwit on Love St.</i> and submit that.</font>

90
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. That settles it.</font>

91
00:06:46,050 --> 00:06:48,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, when you finish your
 manuscript, send it to me.</font>

92
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, once we're done here, 
can someone go help out in the library?</font>

93
00:06:53,850 --> 00:06:55,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help out with what?</font>

94
00:06:55,890 --> 00:07:00,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every year, a club member helps the 
library with collection maintenance.</font>

95
00:07:00,250 --> 00:07:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In exchange, they let us put in requests
 when they order new books.</font>

96
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:08,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it's a "we scratch their back, 
they scratch ours" sort of thing.</font>

97
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:18,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you have a middle school
 reunion party later?</font>

98
00:07:18,830 --> 00:07:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, is Hakamada going?</font>

99
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:23,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. Karen-chan's coming, too.</font>

100
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though Himemiya-san 
was an exchange student?</font>

101
00:07:26,550 --> 00:07:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Among my friends, if we start dating someone, 
we have to introduce them to everyone.</font>

102
00:07:31,730 --> 00:07:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you gonna be okay there?</font>

103
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. I'm no longer the 
same person I was in the first term.</font>

104
00:07:38,770 --> 00:07:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, today I am full of gratitude for all things 
in the world around me, great and small.</font>

105
00:07:44,430 --> 00:07:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have opened my heart to kindness.</font>

106
00:07:46,730 --> 00:07:47,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me?</font>

107
00:07:48,980 --> 00:07:52,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall I explain it in words even you 
can understand, Nukumizu-kun?</font>

108
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't get my hopes up, but sure.</font>

109
00:07:54,250 --> 00:07:58,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you see, Sosuke and Karen-chan 
are both dear friends of mine.</font>

110
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when my dear friends find happiness,
shouldn't that delight me, as well?</font>

111
00:08:05,030 --> 00:08:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Essentially, by going out together, 
those two have blessed me with great joy.</font>

112
00:08:11,050 --> 00:08:14,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At this stage, I feel nothing 
but gratitude toward them.</font>

113
00:08:15,370 --> 00:08:17,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you say so, Yanami-san.</font>

114
00:08:17,470 --> 00:08:20,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should read this as well, Nukumizu-kun.</font>

115
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black">{\an8}<font size="22"><font color="#765d1a">108
 Magic Words
to Lighten 
Your Heart</font></font></font></font>

116
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black">{\an8}<font size="16"><font color="#5e4a10">Umashima San</font></font></font></font>

117
00:08:20,550 --> 00:08:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, what is that book?</font>

118
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you see, it teaches you
 how to accept yourself.</font>

119
00:08:27,380 --> 00:08:30,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to take 
the yakitori off the stick.</font>

120
00:08:30,490 --> 00:08:32,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can eat the whole thing at once.</font>

121
00:08:32,660 --> 00:08:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the sort of wisdom contained within.</font>

122
00:08:35,070 --> 00:08:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right. So it's a self-help book
you read when you've lost it.</i></font>

123
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nukumizu!</font>

124
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you on duty today?</font>

125
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, uh, yeah.</font>

126
00:08:45,690 --> 00:08:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, does this stand out?</font>

127
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:50,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Well, kinda.</font>

128
00:08:50,110 --> 00:08:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a present from Chihaya.</font>

129
00:08:52,050 --> 00:08:55,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She told me never to take it off.
 Like, come on, right?</font>

130
00:08:55,930 --> 00:09:00,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When she gave it to me, she made it 
this big surprise. You know what it's like.</font>

131
00:09:01,130 --> 00:09:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

132
00:09:03,350 --> 00:09:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess that's what they call
 "humble-bragging."</i></font>

133
00:09:06,650 --> 00:09:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still, everyone around me is getting dumped, 
so it was kind of a breath of fresh air.</i></font>

134
00:09:14,040 --> 00:09:15,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What?</font>

135
00:09:15,380 --> 00:09:20,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing. Oh, Komari, you said you'd write 
something new. What are you gonna write?</font>

136
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:24,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A r-reincarnation isekai. R-Romance genre.</font>

137
00:09:24,950 --> 00:09:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I actually started it 
during summer vacation.</font>

